s/gs/righteous-righteousness?lang=ukr\"><small>ПП</small> Праведник, Праведність</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1а","pid":"121083359","context":"співом","text":"<p data-aid=\"121083387\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/sing?lang=ukr\"><small>ПП</small> Співати</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/sing?lang=ukr","text":"ПП Співати"}]},"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2а","pid":"121083360","context":"коли","text":"<p data-aid=\"121083390\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/stake?lang=ukr\"><small>ПП</small> Кіл</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/stake?lang=ukr","text":"ПП Кіл"}]},"note3a":{"id":"note3a","marker":"3а","pid":"121083361","context":"Іновірців","text":"<p data-aid=\"121083392\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gentiles?lang=ukr\"><small>ПП</small> Іновірці</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/gentiles?lang=ukr","text":"ПП Іновірці"}]},"note4a":{"id":"note4a","marker":"4а","pid":"121083362","context":"сорому","text":"<p data-aid=\"121083395\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.7,13?lang=ukr#p7\">2 Неф. 6:7, 13</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/6.7,13?lang=ukr#p7","text":"2 Неф. 6:7, 13"}]},"note8a":{"id":"note8a","marker":"8а","pid":"121083366","context":"милість","text":"<p data-aid=\"121083397\" id=\"note8a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/merciful-mercy?lang=ukr\"><small>ПП</small> Милостивий, Милість</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/merciful-mercy?lang=ukr","text":"ПП Милостивий, Милість"}]},"note9a":{"id":"note9a","marker":"9а","pid":"121083367","context":"це",